ID_SPARTA_PG_SLIDE1_PARAGRAPH: Community games is a way for you to set up your own games with your own set of rules, Create a rotation with your favorite maps & modes or go crazy and create a knife only experience and share it with the Battlefield Community.
ID_SPARTA_PG_SLIDE2_PARAGRAPH: Set up your own configurations (configs) and tailor them to you and your communities wants and needs. You can also use the DICE CONFIGS to quickly set up your Community Game to run with hardcore settings, infantry only settings and much more.
ID_SPARTA_PG_SLIDE3_PARAGRAPH: Whether you’re a fresh recruit or seasoned veteran, Battlefield is for everyone.[[newline]][[newline]]We are committed to maintaining Battlefield V as an inclusive, diverse, and global community. We will take action against any abusive behavior that targets players' race, gender, sexual orientation, religion, heritage, or country of origin, or is otherwise abusive. Learn more in EAs User Agreement[[newline]][[newline]]Help us by reporting problem players or inappropriate content. Learn more at ea.com/positiveplay.
ID_SPARTA_PLATOONS_ABOUT_DISCLAIMER: *FULL PLATOON FUNCTIONALITY AND ACTIVITY IS ONLY AVAILABLE FOR BATTLEFIELD 1.
ID_SPARTA_PLATOONS_ABOUT_DISCLAIMER_EXTR: A SUBSET OF THE FUNCTIONALITY AND ACTIVITY WILL ALSO BE AVAILABLE FOR BATTLEFIELD V.
ID_SPARTA_PLATOONS_ABOUT_MANAGE_DESC: Customize name, tag, emblem, settings and change member ranks at any time, in-game or using the Battlefield Companion.
ID_SPARTA_PLATOONS_ABOUT_PLAY_DESC: We will show you when and where your Platoon is playing, so you can instantly join in on the fun and help them out.
ID_SPARTA_PLATOONS_ABOUT_REPRESENT_DESC: Show off your Platoon tag and emblem, fill a squad and have it renamed to your Platoon, and get Platoon pennants on captured flags.
ID_SPARTA_PLATOONS_ABOUT_SUBTITLE: Making it easier and more fun to play together with your clan and social groups
